According to <br />
@diarioas<br />
, Dani Ceballos is interested in joining Valencia, but Real don't want him to join a domestic rival. #Arsenal are also unwilling to terminate the loan as they will have to sign a replacement.

Arsenal will pay &euro;4m for the loan signing of Flamengo centre-back Pablo Mar&iacute; until July 2020 &amp; have an option to make the deal permanent for a further &euro;4m afterwards, while performance based add-ons, if met, are worth &euro;2m. [<br />
@TiagoSalazar<br />
] #afc

On Wednesday morning, Matt&eacute;o Guendouzi received a video compilation from an Arsenal video analyst straight to his iPhone with footage of every piece of play he was involved in vs Chelsea the previous evening.<br />
<br />
Matt&eacute;o Guendouzi on the footage: &quot;It helps me a lot because when you are on the pitch you are living the match and therefore you don&rsquo;t see what you could&rsquo;ve done better. Was there a player free I should&rsquo;ve looked to? Etc.&quot;
